    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "TheSchrodinger bridge problem can be fully characterized by the initial distribution $\\pmb { p } _ { 0 }$ and the Schrodingerpotential $\\phi ^ { * } ( x ) : \\mathbb { R } ^ { D }  \\mathbb { R } _ { + }$ .The optimal drift can be expressed by the Schrodingerpotentialas ",
