        "img_path": "/data/huangyc/Document2All/posterDataOutput_vlm/Light Schrödinger Bridge_poster/auto/images/equations/equations_1.jpg",
        "text": "$$\n\\mathsf { i n f } _ { T \\in \\mathcal { F } ( p _ { 0 } , p _ { 1 } ) } \\mathsf { K L } ( T | | W ^ { \\epsilon } ) ,\n$$",
        "text_format": "latex",
        "bbox": [
