        "type": "text",
        "text": "ε=0.1 e=1 ∈=10 D=2D=16D=64 D=128 D=2 D=16 D=64 D=128D=2D=16D=64D=128   \nBest solver 1.94 13.67 11.74 11.4 1.04 9.08 18.05 15.23 1.40 1.27 2.36 1.31   \nLightSB] 0.03 0.08 0.28 0.60 0.05 0.09 0.24 0.62 0.07 0.11 0.21 0.37 ±std ±0.01 ±0.04 ±0.02 ±0.02 ±0.003 ±0.006 ±0.007 ±0.007 ±0.02 ±0.01 ±0.01 ±0.01 \\*Themetric cBW-UVP isused for comparising build schrodinger bridge with ground-truth bridge (lower=better). ",
